{"id":90477,"date":"2022-10-02T12:21:13","date_gmt":"2022-10-02T10:21:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=90477"},"modified":"2022-10-02T12:24:28","modified_gmt":"2022-10-02T10:24:28","slug":"theth","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/theth\/","title":{"rendered":"Theth: Most Beautiful Mountain Village in Albania"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"todo\">Things to do in Theth, Albania<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Welcome to Theth&#x2014;a quaint mountain village and one of the best places to visit in all of Albania! The landscape here rivals one you&#x2019;d find in the Swiss Alps; the dramatic peaks of the Accursed Mountains look over the town and green fields filled with cows and goats.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205556\/theth-albania-19.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-91365 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205556\/theth-albania-19.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205556\/theth-albania-19-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205556\/theth-albania-19-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205556\/theth-albania-19-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205556\/theth-albania-19-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205556\/theth-albania-19-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/sta