ows along the remote roads.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20.jpg\" alt=\"theth albania travel\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"theth albania travel\" class=\"wp-image-91367 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205608\/theth-albania-20-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/272056