d to Theth, and you could only reach the village by 4&#xD7;4. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9.jpg\" alt=\"theth things to do albania\"><\/noscript><img width=\"243\" height=\"338\" alt=\"theth things to do albania\" class=\"wp-image-91344 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1379px) 100vw, 1379px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9.jpg 1379w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-431x600.jpg 431w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-582x810.jpg 582w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-243x338.jpg 243w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-117x163.jpg 117w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-129x180.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-552x768.jpg 552w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-735x1024.jpg 735w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-776x1080.jpg 776w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-1034x1440.jpg 1034w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-300x418.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205409\/theth-albania-9-600x835.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content