.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-2-valbone-pass-hike\">2. Valbon&#xEB; Pass&#xA0;Hike<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from the charming village, the area is famous for the Valbon&#xEB; Pass hike, a long walk through the mountains, and one of the most rewarding and beautiful parts of any <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/albania-itinerary\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Albania itinerary<\/a>. The hike moves up through the mountains, passing through forests, grasslands, bubbling streams, and meadows full of flowers and boulders.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205306\/theth-albania-route-19.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-91334 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205306\/theth-albania-route-19.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205306\/theth-albania-route-19-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205306\/theth-albania-route-19-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205306\/theth-albania-route-19-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205306\/theth-albania-route-19-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205306\/theth-albania-route-19-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205306\/theth-albania-route-19-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205306\/theth-albania-route-19-51