" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205619\/theth-albania-21.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h5>Directions to the peak (half-loop)<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>First, walk straight past the mini market until you see the white and red flag signs on your right. Follow these and begin your ascent up through the forest. From the start to the cafe near the top, it takes around 2.5\/3 hours. You can stop here for a drink and a snack and then hike another 45 minutes up to the top of the peak. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8.jpg\" alt=\"restaurant hike theth albania\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"restaurant hike theth albania\" class=\"wp-image-91342 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205357\/theth-albania-8.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>In total, it takes around 4 hours. Once you reach the top of the peak, you&#x2019;ll be rewarded with the most incredible views!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> Be aware that en route, you&#x2019;ll be hiking on steep gravel paths. Always wear good footwear (closed trainers or hiking boots), wear layers of clothing, mosquito repellent, sunscreen, and sunglasses.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>If you want to do the full hike to Valbon&#xEB;, you can carry on from here. There are around 4 cafes on the route, each one with access to spring water, so bring your reusable water bottle, and you can refill it as you go.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/reduce-plastic-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to travel plastic-free!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/90477&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/01135553\/to-do-theth-albania-2.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/01135553\/to-do-theth-albania-2-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/01135553\/to-do-theth-albania-2-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Theth: Most Beautiful Mountain Village in Albania\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-how-to-return-from-valbone-full-hike\">How to return from Valbon&#xEB; (full hike)<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#x2019;re planning on doing the full hike from Valbon&#xEB;, pack a daypack with a change of clothes and leave the rest at your accommodation. This is because we recommend staying the night in Valbon&#xEB; and making the journey back to Theth the next day.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The return journey from  Valbon&#xEB; can be done in 4 stages:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Go by minibus from Valbon&#xEB; to the ferry (1 hour).<\/li><li>Take the ferry from Fierze across the lake to Koman (2.5 hours). This is a beautiful boat ride that will be a highlight of your Albania itinerary. The ferry company &#x2018;<a href=\"https:\/\/komanilakeferry.com\/en\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Berisha<\/a>&#x2018; offers packages, including transfers on either side of the ferry.&#xA0;<\/li><li>From here, you can organize a minibus transfer onto Shkoder (1.5 hours). You can book this with Berisha too.<\/li><li>From Shkoder, it&#x2019;s another 1.5-hour transfer back to Theth (on the newly paved road). You can organize this with your accommodation in Shkoder (normally for around 10 EUR).<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2.jpg\" alt=\"mountain hike theth albania\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"mountain hike theth albania\" class=\"wp-image-91338 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205332\/theth-albania-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h5>Tickets for your return journey<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>You can reserve your minibus and ferry transfer well in advance (make sure to book well ahead if traveling in your own car, as the ferries don&#x2019;t have that much capacity for vehicles).&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, book an organized tour to discover Valbon&#xEB;. This can be easier than organizing your own transfers, as they include your accommodation, transport, as well as a guide to take you through the mountains.<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"107865P44,10132P35,10132P30\" data-vi-campaign=\"theth-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            \n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>You can also do the journey in reverse, starting from Shkoder and ending in Theth. Many people prefer to do the hike this way as it&#x2019;s nicer to get the long journey out the way at the beginning of the trip. The beginning of the path is also said to be easier from Valbon&#xEB;, so you can ease yourself into the hike.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-3-hike-to-theth-waterfall\">3. Hike to Theth Waterfall&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Just 45 minutes from Theth village is the beautiful Grunasi Waterfall, a huge 25-meter-high cascade that falls from a dramatic limestone cliff. It&#x2019;s a 45-minute walk each way that crosses rocky paths and follows along the mountain river before heading up into the woods. As you go, discover wonderful views out across the mountain peaks&#x2014;this is nature at its finest!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27.jpg\" alt=\"things to do theth albania river\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do theth albania river\" class=\"wp-image-91528 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-150x188.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165509\/theth-albania-27.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>When you reach the waterfall, you can swim in the pool below. However, be aware that the water is freezing! If it&#x2019;s the summer, bring your swimsuit and brave the water for a refreshing end to your hike. Because of the water droplets here, you might even be lucky enough to see a rainbow at the foot of the falls.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> We recommend walking to Grunasi Waterfall in the morning to avoid crowds and have the most peaceful hike. This hike is also the beginning of the hike you&#x2019;ll take to the Blue Eye.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-4-discover-the-blue-eye-of-theth-albania\">4. Discover the Blue Eye of Theth, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Albania<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You may have heard of the popular Sarande Blue Eye, but Theth also has its very own Blue Eye. The Blue Eye near Theth (Syri i Kalt&#xEB;r in Albanian) is a deep water pool set deep within limestone rock. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It&#x2019;s said to resemble a blue eye because of its bright blue color in the center that slowly descends out into lighter blues and greens. This incredible color and clear water come as a result of the depth of the water and the vegetation surrounding it, making it one of the most blissful places to swim. Plus, there&#x2019;s also a waterfall that cascades down into the pool below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3.jpg\" alt=\"blue eye albania travel guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"blue eye albania travel guide\" class=\"wp-image-88125 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-150x225.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/17115522\/blue-eye-albania-route-3.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Blue Eye near Theth is high up in the mountains and much higher than the one at Sarande, making it even colder, but it&#x2019;s still worth it for a refreshing dip (although we wouldn&#x2019;t recommend swimming outside of the summer months). What&#x2019;s more, make sure to visit before 3 PM, as after this time the sun sets behind the mountains, and it will be very cold. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/butrint-national-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Butrint National Park, Albania<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-how-to-reach-the-blue-eye-of-theth\">How to reach the Blue Eye of Theth<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The hike from Theth itself to the Blue Eye is around 6-7 hours (3 hours each way) and covers a total of 17km. Although it&#x2019;s a long hike, it&#x2019;s very beautiful and is a mainly flat route, so it can be done by all levels of hikers. The only steep bit is towards the end, where you ascend to the Blue Eye itself. There are also cafes en route, so you can stop for drinks or a bite to eat as you go.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23.jpg\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia hiking\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do minca colombia hiking\" class=\"wp-image-88414 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-150x194.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22143059\/minca-colombia-23.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h5>Driving to the Blue Eye<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>Don&#x2019;t fancy the long hike? The alternative is to drive to the village of Nderlysaj and start the hike from there. This hike is only 40 minutes (one way), so it&#x2019;s much more achievable and will leave you more of the day to do other activities in the area. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>If you don&#x2019;t have a car, you can take a taxi from Theth and ask them to wait for you in the village (this can cost a lot as they&#x2019;ll have to wait for a few hours) or arrange taxis both ways (sometimes there are shared options available to lower costs). You can also visit the Blue Eye as part of a tour, including return transportation.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-vi-partner-id=\"P00037894\" data-vi-language=\"en\" data-vi-currency=\"USD\" data-vi-partner-type=\"AFFILIATE\" data-vi-url=\"150064P2,16080P5\" data-vi-campaign=\"theth-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-viator\" data-script=\"https:\/\/www.viator.com\/orion\/partner\/widget.js\"><\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30.jpg\" alt=\"things to do theth albania car\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do theth albania car\" class=\"wp-image-91540 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-150x188.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110710\/theth-albania-30.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-5-visit-the-church-in-theth\">5. Visit the Church in Theth<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>This beautiful church is an icon of Theth and truly looks like something out of a fairytale. The grey-tiled roofed church sits in the middle of an open meadow, surrounded by towering mountain peaks and wildflowers. The story goes that people originally came to Theth to practice their faith undisturbed in the peace of nature, and it&#x2019;s easy to see why!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18.jpg\" alt=\"theth albania church horse\"><\/noscript><img width=\"252\" height=\"338\" alt=\"theth albania church horse\" class=\"wp-image-91363 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1429px) 100vw, 1429px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18.jpg 1429w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-447x600.jpg 447w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-603x810.jpg 603w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-252x338.jpg 252w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-121x163.jpg 121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-134x180.jpg 134w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-572x768.jpg 572w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-762x1024.jpg 762w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-804x1080.jpg 804w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-1072x1440.jpg 1072w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-300x403.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-600x806.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-150x202.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18-22x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205544\/theth-albania-18.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The church dates all the way back to 1892, and over the years, it has been a school and even a health center during the communist regime. Nowadays, it&#x2019;s still used by locals as a place of worship, visible from all around with its rooftop cross.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-91530 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/30165524\/theth-albania-28-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/