              <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/albania-itinerary\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Albania 2-week road trip itinerary!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10.jpg\" alt=\"theth albania things to do\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"theth albania things to do\" class=\"wp-image-91346 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-150x188.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205421\/theth-albania-10.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"restaurants\">Best Cafes and Restaurants in Theth<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The food in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Albania<\/a> is varied but is generally quite meat-heavy, although there are some veggie options among the traditional dishes. Theth, however, is very small and remote, meaning there aren&#x2019;t that many restaurants in the village, and it&#x2019;s the most difficult place to get veggie food. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23.jpg\" alt=\"best restaurant theth albania\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"308\" alt=\"best restaurant theth albania\" class=\"wp-image-91372 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-800x548.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-1080x739.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-450x308.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-163x112.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-263x180.jpg 263w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-768x526.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-1024x701.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-1440x986.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-300x205.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-600x411.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-150x103.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23-30x21.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205633\/theth-albania-23.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Despite this, in every guesthouse and hotel, you&#x2019;ll find a small restaurant\/cafe where you can enjoy typical food and drink from Albania (and they&#x2019;re all very accommodating about veggie options). Either eat at your hotel or spend your days in Theth jumping between the others, deciding which one is your favorite.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>If you&#x2019;re looking for a good cup of coffee, we think the best coffee was at the place we stayed: Gurra Family Guesthouse. There is also one small supermarket in Theth if you need snacks (especially for hiking!).<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip:<\/strong> you can drink tap water in Albania. Refill your reusable water bottle at your hotel and help <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/plastic-alternatives-zero-waste\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">reduce plastic waste<\/a>!<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"hotels\">Where to Stay in Theth, Albania<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As Theth is such a beautiful mountainous region, it&#x2019;s very popular for people wanting to camp and enjoy nature. There are plenty of campsites in Theth itself and the surrounding areas, all with great amenities.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if you want something a little more comfortable, there are lots of charming guesthouses and hotels in Theth. Everything is very rustic and &#x2018;chalet-like&#x2019;, in keeping with the traditional mountain way of life. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12.jpg\" alt=\"best hotel theth albania\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best hotel theth albania\" class=\"wp-image-91350 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-791x1024.jpg 791w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-835x1080.jpg 835w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205446\/theth-albania-12-1113x1440.jpg 1113w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.co