xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-albania\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your flight to Tirana<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>By Car<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best way to visit Theth is by car. In the past, the last part of the road to Theth wasn&#x2019;t paved, so it required a 4&#xD7;4. Recently, the road has been paved, so it can now be driven on by any car. You&#x2019;ll only need a stronger\/better car when driving past the town of Theth, for example, Lumi i Shale. Having your own vehicle also gives you the flexibility to explore the area and road trip using our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/albania-itinerary\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">2-week Albania itinerary<\/a>.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p>Rent a car in Albania via&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-albania\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sunny Cars<\/a>. Free cancellation up to 1 hour before rental start and insurances are included (so no surprises when collecting your car).&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-albania\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29.jpg\" alt=\"road to theth albania\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"road to theth albania\" class=\"wp-image-91538 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-150x188.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/01110654\/theth-albania-29.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>By Minivan<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you don&#x2019;t have a car, you can arrange a transfer with your guesthouse in Theth or ask your hotel\/guesthouse in Shkoder to request a pick-up by shared bus. It will normally collect you between 7 AM &#x2013; 8 AM in the morning, and it takes about 3 hours to reach Theth. The price is 1200 LEK (10 EUR) per person for a one-way transfer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Organized Tour<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, you can book an organized tour that will take you to Theth and include other sights in the area too. It&#x2019;s a great way to meet people and learn more about the area from a local guide!<\/p>\n\n\n\n                <div data-gyg-href=\"https:\/\/widget.getyourguide.com\/default\/activities.frame\" data-gyg-locale-code=\"en-US\" data-gyg-widget=\"activities\" data-gyg-number-of-items=\"3\" data-gyg-tour-ids=\"409570,396197,418869\" data-gyg-partner-id=\"SYAMOP2\" data-gyg-cmp=\"theth-widget\" class=\"lazyload block-getyourguide\" data-script=\"https:\/\/widget.getyourguide.com\/dist\/pa.umd.production.min.js\"><\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Getting Around Theth<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#x2019;ll spend most of your time in Theth hiking. If you have a car, it makes it easier to visit places like the Blue Eye. However, if you don&#x2019;t, it&#x2019;s no problem as your guesthouse will be able to arrange a local taxi for you.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"budget\">How Much Does Theth Cost?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The prices are very reasonable in Theth, although be aware that in summer the mountains are a popular destination for tourists so hotel rooms may raise in price. However, enjoying nature is totally free!&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Because the village is so remote, there are no ATMs in the area, so you&#x2019;ll need to bring enough cash with you to last your trip or pay with a Wise card. If you don&#x2019;t have a Wise Card, Credins bank is the only one that doesn&#x2019;t seem to charge an absurd amount of fee to take out money. We also recommend always paying in LEK as everyone keeps their own conversion rate to Euros.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-budget\">\n        <span class=\"block-budget__title\">Budget<\/span><ul class=\"block-budget__list\"><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hotels: 30 &#x2013; 100 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Guesthouses: 25 &#x2013; 40 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--restaurants\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Price per meal: 5 &#x2013; 15 USD\n                    <\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Budget Tip:<\/strong> The Albanian currency is LEK, but Euros are also accepted. Save on exchange fees by converting your own local currency to LEK\/EUR with a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\">Wise card<\/a>. You can use this card to withdraw from the ATM in Albania or pay by card at most shops. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\">Get a Wise card here; it&#x2019;s free!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205319\/theth-albania-1.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"248\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-91336 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1409px) 100vw, 1409px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205319\/theth-albania-1.jpg 1409w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205319\/theth-albania-1-440x600.jpg 440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205319\/theth-albania-1-594x810.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205319\/theth-albania-1-248x338.jpg 248w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205319\/theth-albania-1-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205319\/theth-albania-1-120x163.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205319\/theth-albania-1-132x180.jpg 132w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/27205319\/theth-albania-1-564x768.jp