ember, it&#x2019;s a much higher altitude in Theth, so bring plenty of layers as it can get cooler at night.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Things to do in Theth, Albania Welcome to Theth&#x2014;a quaint mountain village and one of the best places to visit in all of Albania! The landscape here rivals one you&#x2019;d find in the Swiss Alps; the dramatic peaks of the Accursed Mountains look over the town and green fields filled with cows and goats.&#xA0; 1. [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":91346,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","_relevanssi_related_posts":"87403,83416,88174,56690,82848,66281"},"categories":[7313,4750,9],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Theth: Most Beautiful Mountain Town in Albania \u00b7 Salt in our Hair<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Discover beautiful Theth, a traditional village nestled in the Albanian Alps. Find out all you need to know about visiting Theth, Albania!\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/albania\/theth\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Theth: Most Beautiful Mountain Village in Albania\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Things to do in Theth, Albania Welcome to Theth\